          },
          "text": "Dear Elon and the SpaceX Team,\nMy name is RyougiShiki.\nI am writing with a heavy heart. Recently, a very dear friend of mine passed away after a long and painful battle with severe depression and Bertolotti syndrome, a congenital spinal condition that caused her immense suffering. She called herself 炽烈已极 @AnIncandescence. She deeply loved Mars, especially the Tharsis region. She often dreamed of one day seeing or exploring that dramatic and awe-inspiring landscape.\nIf there is any possibility in the future Starship missions or Mars exploration plans that your team could land in or explore the Tharsis area, it would carry profound meaning for me and for everyone who loved her. It would be a beautiful and lasting way to honor her passion and her memory.\nAdditionally, her X account @AnIncandescence has been suspended. That account holds many precious memories we shared. If there is any way it could be reviewed and reinstated, it would mean a great deal to her friends who miss her terribly.\nThank you for your tireless work to make humanity a multi-planetary species. Your vision gave people like her something extraordinary to dream about, even in the darkest times. It continues to give all of us hope.\nWith sincere gratitude and support,\nRyougiShiki\n\n亲爱的Elon先生与SpaceX团队：\n\n我叫RyougiShiki。\n\n我怀着沉重的心情写下这封信。最近，我一位非常亲密的朋友在与严重抑郁症以及Bertolotti综合征（这是一种先天性脊柱疾病）长期而痛苦的斗争后离世。她的X账号是 @AnIncandescence，她称自己为“炽烈已极”。她非常热爱火星，尤其是Tharsis区域。她常常梦想有一天能够亲眼看到，甚至探索那片极具震撼力的地貌。\n\n如果未来的星舰任务或火星探索计划中，有任何可能将探测或着陆点设定在Tharsis区域，这对我以及所有爱她的人来说都将具有深远的意义。这将成为一种美丽而持久的方式，去纪念她的热爱与记忆。\n\n此外，她的X账号 @AnIncandescence 已被暂停。那个账号承载着许多我们共同的珍贵回忆。如果有任何方式可以重新审核并恢复它，对她的朋友们来说将意义重大，我们都非常想念她。\n\n感谢你们为让人类成为多行星物种所付出的不懈努力。你们的愿景曾给予像她这样的人一种极其特别的梦想，即使在最黑暗的时刻也能继续前行。它也依然在为我们所有人带来希望。\n\n致以诚挚的感谢与支持，\nRyougiShiki\n\n@elonmusk @SpaceX \n #Mars #Tharsis #SpaceX"
        },
